If you have done the map walthrough, and wanted to extend it
just for location, this might be the repo for you.  This is 
a working map demo that places the android logo in your current
location, after it adjust the map to fit your area.

= Installing
Clont his repo, import the project into your workspace, navigate
to res/layout/ and rename main.xml.example to main.xml.  Adjust with 
your map key, and run it on an emulator or device of your choosing.

Feel free to enhance and make suggestions, fork it, or whatevr.

* References:

http://developer.android.com/resources/tutorials/views/hello-mapview.html
http://www.vogella.de/articles/AndroidLocationAPI/article.html

Cheers.

Jeff A.
